PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F354A1774534302
OL,3,CStreeting: North Cumbria NHS Trust is
OL,4,Cone of the 'worst services in the
OL,5,Ccountry'
OL,7,FNorth Cumbria Integrated Care NHS
OL,8,FFoundation Trust (NCIC) will be put
OL,9,Finto a recovery programme as the
OL,10,Fgovernment plans to tackle the "worst
OL,11,Fservices in the country".
OL,13,FHealth Secretary Wes Streeting said
OL,14,F"failure has been tolerated for too
OL,15,Flong", as he named five NHS trusts
OL,16,Fthat will be placed in the 'NHS
OL,17,FIntensive Recovery programme'.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G1/13
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BBorder NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,355,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35402
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F354A1774534302
OL,3,CStreeting: North Cumbria NHS Trust is
OL,4,Cone of the 'worst services in the
OL,5,Ccountry'
OL,7,FHe said that despite improvement
OL,8,Facross the NHS overall, as shown with
OL,9,Fa rise in public satisfaction with the
OL,10,Fservice in the latest British Social
OL,11,FAttitudes Survey, some "challenged"
OL,12,Ftrusts have continued to struggle.
OL,14,FNCIC was rated as the fourth-worst NHS
OL,15,Ftrust in the country when the first
OL,16,Fleague tables were released in 2025.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G2/13
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BBorder NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,355,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35403
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F354A1774534302
OL,3,CStreeting: North Cumbria NHS Trust is
OL,4,Cone of the 'worst services in the
OL,5,Ccountry'
OL,7,FThe Department of Health and Social
OL,8,FCare said the new programme has
OL,9,Fidentified trusts at the bottom of the
OL,10,FNHS league tables where patients face
OL,11,Fthe longest waits for care, there are
OL,12,Fpersistent financial problems and high
OL,13,Fleadership "churn".
OL,15,FThe department said that the trusts
OL,16,Fidentified are not failing through
OL,17,Flack of effort but they face "deep-
OL,18,Frooted challenges", including
OL,19,F"structural constraints and financial
OL,20,Fimbalance".
OL,26,@{D@AOU
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G3/13
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BBorder NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,355,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35404
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F354A1774534302
OL,3,CStreeting: North Cumbria NHS Trust is
OL,4,Cone of the 'worst services in the
OL,5,Ccountry'
OL,7,FMr Streeting will announce plans to
OL,8,F"get these trusts up to standard
OL,9,Fagain", the department said.
OL,11,FThe programme will begin in April and
OL,12,Fwill see each organisation receive a
OL,13,Ftailored improvement approach,
OL,14,Fincluding a change of leadership where
OL,15,Fnecessary, NHS "veterans" with a
OL,16,Fhistory of success brought into
OL,17,Funderperforming areas, and the merging
OL,18,For separating of trusts and cash for
OL,19,Fcrumbling estates.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G4/13
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BBorder NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,355,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35405
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F354A1774534302
OL,3,CStreeting: North Cumbria NHS Trust is
OL,4,Cone of the 'worst services in the
OL,5,Ccountry'
OL,7,FSpeaking on Wednesday March 25, Mr
OL,8,FStreeting said: "Right now, a cluster
OL,9,Fof high-performing trusts are masking
OL,10,Fsome chronic under-performance in
OL,11,Fother parts of the country.
OL,13,F"Failure has been tolerated for too
OL,14,Flong. Staff know it. Patients feel it.
OL,15,FAnd I won't stand for it.
OL,17,F"We won't have succeeded in changing
OL,18,Fthe NHS until we change it for the
OL,19,Fpatients who are suffering the worst
OL,20,Fservices in the country.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G5/13
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BBorder NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,355,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35406
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F354A1774534302
OL,3,CStreeting: North Cumbria NHS Trust is
OL,4,Cone of the 'worst services in the
OL,5,Ccountry'
OL,7,F"In some places, so many years of poor
OL,8,Fservice without improvement is feeding
OL,9,Fthat sense of fatalism. They believe
OL,10,Fthat after so long, it just can't get
OL,11,Fbetter - in fact, they've never seen
OL,12,Fit get better.
OL,14,F"That's why I've announced today a new
OL,15,Fintensive recovery programme. This
OL,16,Fwill target the worst performing
OL,17,Fproviders, sending in our best leaders
OL,18,For delivering the structural changes
OL,19,Fnecessary to get them back on track.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G6/13
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BBorder NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,355,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35407
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F354A1774534302
OL,3,CStreeting: North Cumbria NHS Trust is
OL,4,Cone of the 'worst services in the
OL,5,Ccountry'
OL,7,F"No more turning a blind eye to
OL,8,Ffailure."
OL,10,FIt comes after the latest British
OL,11,FSocial Attitudes Survey revealed that
OL,12,Fsatisfaction with the NHS has risen
OL,13,Ffor the first time since before the
OL,14,FCovid-19 pandemic.
OL,16,FBut experts said that improvements
OL,17,Fwere "fragile" because the public was
OL,18,Fstill largely "unhappy" about the
OL,19,Fservice in 2025.
OL,26,@pD@IO]
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G7/13
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BBorder NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,355,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35408
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F354A1774534302
OL,3,CStreeting: North Cumbria NHS Trust is
OL,4,Cone of the 'worst services in the
OL,5,Ccountry'
OL,7,FPublic satisfaction with the NHS
OL,8,Fdipped to a record low in 2024, with
OL,9,Fsome 21% of people satisfied with the
OL,10,Fhealth service.
OL,12,FThe latest survey, which ran between
OL,13,FAugust and October last year, found
OL,14,Fthis rose by five percentage points to
OL,15,F26%, according to analysis from the
OL,16,FKing's Fund and the Nuffield Trust
OL,17,Fthink tanks.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G8/13
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BBorder NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,355,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35409
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F354A1774534302
OL,3,CStreeting: North Cumbria NHS Trust is
OL,4,Cone of the 'worst services in the
OL,5,Ccountry'
OL,7,FIn response Trudie Davies, Chief
OL,8,FExecutive at NCIC said: "We are
OL,9,Fputting in place the resources we need
OL,10,Fto improve access to urgent and
OL,11,Femergency care so that we can see more
OL,12,Fpatients, in a timely way, in the
OL,13,Fright clinical setting.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G9/13
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BBorder NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,355,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35410
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F354A1774534302
OL,3,CStreeting: North Cumbria NHS Trust is
OL,4,Cone of the 'worst services in the
OL,5,Ccountry'
OL,7,F"We know that our current A&E
OL,8,Fdepartment in Carlisle is too small
OL,9,Ffor the volume of patients we see
OL,10,Fwhich leads to delays and
OL,11,Fovercrowding. Our new Urgent Treatment
OL,12,FCentre, a bigger Same Day Emergency
OL,13,FCare department and an expanded acute
OL,14,Fmedical workforce equipped to make key
OL,15,Fdecisions, will be transformative.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                G10/13
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BBorder NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,355,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35411
SC,0011
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F354A1774534302
OL,3,CStreeting: North Cumbria NHS Trust is
OL,4,Cone of the 'worst services in the
OL,5,Ccountry'
OL,7,F"We have an ageing population in
OL,8,FCumbria and many of the patients we
OL,9,Fsee in A&E are frail and elderly. A
OL,10,Fhospital stay is not always the best
OL,11,Foutcome for these patients, which is
OL,12,Fwhy we are investing in our Frailty
OL,13,FSDEC units in Carlisle and Whitehaven.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                G11/13
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BBorder NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,355,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35412
SC,0012
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F354A1774534302
OL,3,CStreeting: North Cumbria NHS Trust is
OL,4,Cone of the 'worst services in the
OL,5,Ccountry'
OL,7,F"Recruiting experienced doctors can be
OL,8,Fa challenge in Cumbria and this leads
OL,9,Fto instability in our clinical teams
OL,10,Fand higher costs as we rely on agency
OL,11,Fand locum staff. We are putting in
OL,12,Fplace a specialist medical recruitment
OL,13,Fteam to help us develop an attraction
OL,14,Fplan based on all the great things
OL,15,FCumbria has to offer.
OL,17,F"As we discuss this major new
OL,18,Finvestment, I want to pay tribute to
OL,19,Four dedicated, hardworking staff who
OL,20,Fshow commitment on a daily basis
OL,21,Fdespite the challenges they face.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                G12/13
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BBorder NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,355,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35413
SC,0013
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F354A1774534302
OL,3,CStreeting: North Cumbria NHS Trust is
OL,4,Cone of the 'worst services in the
OL,5,Ccountry'
OL,7,F"This new package will mean that they
OL,8,Fare supported to deliver the very best
OL,9,Fcare to our patients."
OL,11,FReporting History sees journalists
OL,12,Fjoin News At Ten anchor Tom Bradby to
OL,13,Frevisit their remarkable on-the-day
OL,14,Freports of the defining events of the
OL,15,Fmodern age. Listen to the episodes
OL,16,Fbelow...
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                G13/13
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
